            </table>
            
            <div class="feature-box" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                <h4>‚ö†Ô∏è Important NC Insurance Laws</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>You must carry proof of insurance at all times while driving</li>
                    <li>Driving without insurance: $50-$150 fine + license suspension</li>
                    <li>You have 30 days to notify DMV of any insurance changes</li>
                    <li>NC uses a "fault" system - at-fault driver pays for damages</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

